\fs76\fsmilli38400 \AppleTypeServices \cf0 \cb2 \strokec3 Types of Cybersecurity\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs40\fsmilli20400 \cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa816\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf0 \cb2 Cybersecurity is a broad field that comprises a range of practices, technologies, and strategies to protect digital assets.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \cb2 The image below displays the seven types of cybersecurity.\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs30 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf0 \cb2 \strokec3 Network Security
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \'a0focuses on securing the computer networks and systems from unauthorized access, data theft, and other security breaches. It consists of securing the routers, switches, firewalls, and other network devices from cyberattacks.\
\

\f0\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 Mobile Security
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \'a0has become an important category of cybersecurity due to growing use of mobile devices to access the internet and conduct business transactions. It involves protecting mobile devices, applications, and networks from cyberattacks.\
\

\f0\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 Application Security
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \'a0deals with securing software applications that run on the computer systems, including desktop, mobile, and web-based applications. It involves securing the code, database, and application servers from vulnerabilities that could be exploited by hackers.\
\

\f0\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 Physical Security
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \'a0involves securing the physical infrastructure of digital systems, including data centers, server rooms, and network closets. It includes security measures such as access control, surveillance, and monitoring.\
\

\f0\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 Information Security\'a0
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 involves securing the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of data. It includes security measures such as encryption, access control, backup, and recovery.\
\

\f0\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 Disaster Recovery and Business Continuity
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \'a0focuses on planning and implementing strategies to recover from the cyberattacks and other disasters. It includes different security measures such as backup and recovery, disaster recovery planning, and business continuity planning.\
\

\f0\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 Cloud Security\'a0
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 become a critical area of cybersecurity with the growing use of cloud computing services. It involves protecting cloud-based data storage, processing, and access from cyber threats.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

