\f0\b Cloud Security Alliance (CSA)
\f1\b0 \'a0is a nonprofit organization that promotes research into security best practices for cloud computing and using cloud technologies to secure other forms of computing. CSA offers membership to any interested parties with the relevant expertise to contribute to cloud computing security.\cb1 \strokec3 \
