\f1\b0 is a division of the Department of Homeland Security (DHS) responsible for defending the Internet\'92s infrastructure and improving its security and resilience. It helps protect against infrastructure threats originating from natural disasters, terrorist attacks, cyberwarfare, etc.\cb1 \
