\f0\b \cb2 \strokec3 Insider Threat\'a0
\f1\b0 \cb2 \strokec3 is a security risk that originates from within an organization. It can be intentional or unintentional, and can be motivated by a variety of factors, such as financial gain, ideology, or revenge.\'a0\
Insider threats can be a major security risk for organizations, as they can often bypass security controls and gain access to sensitive data or systems.\
