\fs40\fsmilli20400 \cf0 \cb2 \strokec3 An organization can take a few steps to mitigate the risk of insider threats, including conducting background checks on employees and contractors, implementing security policies and procedures, providing security training to employees, monitoring employee activity, and responding to security incidents promptly and effectively.\'a0\cb1 \
