\cf0 \cb2 The\'a0
\f0\b \cb2 \strokec3 Perimeter-based Security
\f1\b0 \cb2 \strokec3 \'a0model was the dominant security model for many years. It is the traditional model which prevents external attackers from accessing the organization's network.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
